cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques applied to clinical notes for patient classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. Additionally, the paper deals with classification tasks, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with healthcare data, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
